videos.description: Shamorie Ponds pokes it away from RJ Barrett and feeds Marvin Clark II for the layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: St. John's turns steal into and-1 layup

videos.description: Cam Reddish drives to the hoop and Marvin Clark II is called for a flagrant foul on the play.
videos.headline: Red Storm's Clark called for flagrant foul on Reddish drive

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets a steal and throws down a powerful dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Zion takes flight for monstrous slam

videos.description: Zion Williamson goes barreling down the lane and finishes a contested lay-in over a defender.
videos.headline: Zion drives to finish layup

videos.description: Zion Williamson steals a pass and rises up for a one-handed dunk before halftime.
videos.headline: Zion hammers down highlight-reel jam

videos.description: Zion Williamson scores 19 points, including multiple dunks, as Duke leads St. John's 47-37 at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion's dunks highlight 19-point first half vs. St. John's) 2019/2/2 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion's dunks highlight 19-point first half vs. St. John's

videos.description: Zion Williamson gets a steal off a St. John's rebound and finishes a layup, adding a trip to the foul line.
videos.headline: Zion's steal leads to and-1 layup

videos.description: The Red Storm's Justin Simon drives and Zion Williamson blocks the layup attempt out of bounds.
videos.headline: Zion spikes St. John's layup out of bounds

videos.description: Cam Reddish misses the 3-pointer, but Zion Williamson grabs the rebound and powers down a dunk.
videos.headline: Zion cleans up Reddish's missed 3-pointer

videos.description: St. John's guard Shamorie Ponds has a wide-open lane to the hoop and gets stuffed by the rim.
videos.headline: Red Storm's Ponds botches wide-open bucket

videos.description: Zion Williamson and Tre Jones react to Duke's blowout win over St. John's.
videos.headline: Zion: I'm doing 'whatever I can to win'

videos.description: Zion Williamson puts on a dunking clinic and scores a game-high 29 points as Duke blows out St. John's 91-61.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Zion's thunderous dunks highlight Duke's blowout win) 2019/02/02 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Zion's thunderous dunks highlight Duke's blowout win

videos.description: Dick Vitale admires Zion Williamson's athletic ability on some of his big-time dunks.
videos.headline: Vitale gushes over Zion

videos.description: Zion Williamson's mom says her son is a "mama's boy" and that they enjoy watching Naruto together.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_Interview (Zion's mom calls him a 'mama's boy') 2019/02/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: Zion's mom calls him a 'mama's boy'
